
Using Port Driver >> Port_config.h >> You can configure Microcontroller Pins to be Input or Output by writing 0 in front of it for Input and 1 for output

Also in the Same file ,, you can configure input pins to activate Pull up by writing 1 in front of Input Pin initial Value

ex_1 : Set Pin 2 at Port C to be input and Activate Pull up to it : 
from (Port_Config.h) File : apply following Configuration
#define PORTC_PIN2_DIR              0
#define PORTC_PIN2_INITIAL_VAL      1

ex_2 : Set Pin 4 at Port D to be Output:
from (Port_Config.h) File : apply following Configuration
#define PORTD_PIN4_DIR              1


